WEBVTT

1
00:46:53.570 --> 00:46:55.860 
那老家伙都不知道那是什么
Poor dear didn't even know what it was.

2
00:46:56.030 --> 00:46:58.150 
太浪费了 它不应该在那个不长草的地方
It's a waste. It shouldn't spend its life...

3
00:46:58.320 --> 00:47:02.530 
度过它的一生
...on a wall in wherever the hell we were.

4
00:47:02.990 --> 00:47:05.830 
它应该属于我们 我们可以打理好它
It should be with us. We have to to look after it properly.

5
00:47:05.910 --> 00:47:08.040 
我们解放了它      解放?!
We liberated it.        Liberated!

6
00:47:08.290 --> 00:47:09.460 
这个词太传神了
That's one word for it.

7
00:47:09.500 --> 00:47:12.750 
别这么小资 珍妮 你很聪明的
Don't be bourgeois, Jenny. You're better than that.

8
00:47:14.090 --> 00:47:18.050 
不管我给你倒了什么 你都能一口干杯
You drink everything I put in front of you down in one...

9
00:47:18.220 --> 00:47:21.340 
然后把杯子砸在吧台上 要求再来一杯
...and you slam your glass down on the bar and ask for more.

10
00:47:21.890 --> 00:47:23.470 
真很棒
It's wonderful.

